"characterId":201,"voiceId":"main002-1-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"まりな","body":"もう１つは……『Pastel＊Palettes（パステルパレット）』。\n芸能事務所に所属してる子たちで結成された、\nいわゆるアイドルバンドだね","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"main002-1-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"まりな","body":"でも、メンバーの子たちはしっかり演奏もできるみたい。\n有名子役だった白鷺千聖がメンバーに入ったことも\n話題になったバンドだね","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"main002-1-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"まりな","body":"それから、ちょっと変わり種なのがハロー、ハッピーワールド！\nボーカルの弦巻こころって子が『世界中を笑顔にしたい！』って\n思いで結成させたバンドなんだって！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"main002-1-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"まりな","body":"幼稚園や小児科とかでライブをやってるから\n小さい子に人気みたいだけど、\n楽曲のクオリティは私達でも楽しめるものだよ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"main002-1-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"chara